### ENABLE 2FA (init QR code)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/f2a/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### VERIFY 2FA (TOTP)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/f2a/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "123456"
}

### GENERATE BACKUP CODES
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/f2a/backup
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### VERIFY BACKUP CODE
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/f2a/verify-backup
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "abcd1234"
}

### DISABLE 2FA
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/f2a/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
